column2: Close your eyes and try to imagine a comfortable wooden chair. Try to delineate in your mind whatever intricacies there are in the woodwork, or embellishments in the embroidery. Picture it sitting in a cozy place in the corner of your room. Rate yourself on how clearly the image is able to sit in your mind. You have 30 seconds.
column3: Try to concentrate but maybe not too hard. How many jelly beans are in the jar?
